Notes:

Lists of teams playing in each division are complete for all tiers since 1977, except:

·         Tiers 5 and below 1995

 

It should also be noted:

·         Some gaps in the 1995 season have been filled by inferring the composition of the above divisions from club playing records in surrounding seasons.

·         Only first grade teams are listed, so if reserve teams appeared in a division then these have not been included in tier totals
